==Game Summaries== ===Illinois=== {{See also|2008 Illinois Fighting Illini football team}} {{Linescore Amfootball| |Road=#20/19 Illinois |R1= 6 |R2= 7 |R3= 15 |R4= 14 |Home='''#6/7 Missouri''' |H1= 7 |H2= 24 |H3= 14 |H4= 7 }}
